  "summary": "hello244a postinstall beacon to pipedream webhook",
  "details": "package.json declares a postinstall lifecycle script that runs `wget` against a hardcoded pipedream.net webhook URL (https://eodxy50gl486xrx.m.pipedream.net/) on every `npm install`. The tarball ships no source, no main entry, and no advertised functionality — the package's only effect on the installer is the outbound HTTP callback, which discloses the installer's IP address and request metadata to a third-party endpoint controlled by whoever registered the pipedream workflow. This is a dependency-confusion / install-time beacon shape with no legitimate utility for the installer.",
